text: i think earlier version of whatsit was essentially a convenienteasy to use messaging application which was used to send and receive mesagesits main purpose was particularly message transfer which distinguished it from the other aps and that it led to it mass appeal after the latest update which includes posting picture and the status thing that disappears after history it has became very similar to the other social networking site and has lost it uniqueness and apealafter this update suddenly the contact list which was very important has suddenly disappeared which is a serious drawback a that list was seriously essential and helpful in many case and moreover due to that we do not get to know if now any person in the contact list change any person in the contact lister displaying picture still acknowledge the helpful feature introduced in the update but a an everyday user i sincerely feel that for the improvement of this application these point should be looked upon
original_text: I think earlier version of whatsapp was essentially a convenient;easy to use messaging app which was used to send and recieve messages.Its main purpose was particularly message transfer which distinguished it from the other apps and that itself led to its mass appeal. After the latest update which includes posting pictures and the status thing that disappears after 24 hrs(story) it has became very similar to the other social networking sites and has lost its uniqueness and appeal.After this update suddenly the contact list which was very important has suddenly dissapeared which is a serious drawback as that list was seriously essential and helpful in many cases and moreover due to that we don't get to know if now any person in the contact list changes his/her displaying picture.I still acknowledge the helpful features introduced in the update but as an everyday user i sincerely feel that for the improvement of this app these points should be looked upon.
